yayzors!?! this is my 1st map, it took longer than it looks lol. i tried to be creative and use things that worked on other maps on our server such as battle points, a gun room, jail, and a place thats kinda hard to get to. i would like to thank Kate for helping me play-test it and 4ngryToasters for telling me how to make a door and the wonder of the func_detail. Enjoy!
